                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 682</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On June 2, the Department of State announced that because of conditions currently
                    existing in Czechoslovakia, American passports <pb facs="0403" n="1369"
                        xml:id="pg_1369"/> of private travelers were no longer valid to proceed to
                    that country. For the text of the brief Department statement to the press, see
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, June 11, 1951, page
                    932.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
